# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  DiffGI project page — .gitignore
#  Only the self-contained `docs/` folder is meant to be published.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Source / working materials (NOT needed for the published page).
# Contains personal CVs and third-party figures — must stay private.
paper/

# Hard block: never commit personal résumé / CV files, wherever they live.
*cv*.pdf
*CV*.pdf
*[Rr]esume*.pdf
*[Rr]ésumé*.pdf

# Backup of the original (pre-edit) teaser — not used by the live site.
docs/static/videos/teaser_original.mp4

# Demo model weights — host on Hugging Face / CDN, never in the repo
# (GitHub Pages: 100MB/file, ~1GB repo, fair-use bandwidth).
# Curated preset input images under docs/demo/presets/ are fine to commit.
docs/demo/models/
*.onnx
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.pt
*.pth

# ── OS / editor cruft ──────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*~
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# ── misc ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
node_modules/
__pycache__/
